text: Dariusz Garbocz (born 11 January 1971), is a Polish former ice hockey player. He played for GKS Tychy, KKH Katowice, and VIK Västerås HK during his career. He also played for the Polish national team at the 1992 Winter Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:GKS Katowice (ice hockey) players Category:GKS Tychy (ice hockey) players Category:Ice hockey players at the 1992 Winter Olympics Category:Naprzód Janów players Category:Olympic ice hockey players of Poland Category:Polish ice hockey defencemen Category:Sportspeople from Katowice Category:VIK Västerås HK players Category:Polish expatriate sportspeople in Sweden
